These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, dancer, nurse, analyst
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, march, october
1. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the dancer##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
5. the nurse is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's birthday is in october is between the analyst and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| Job   | nurse | architect  | dancer   | analyst    |
| Birthday     | july     | march    | october    | september      |

