.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, software-developer, dancer, police-officer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, tulip, marigold, amaryllis
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the police-officer is the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the dancer is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the software-developer is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
7. the person who growssunflower is between the police-officer and the software-developer##2
8. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growstulip and the dancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Job         | police-officer | dancer   | software-developer | coach  |
| Flower   | marigold     | sunflower | amaryllis  | tulip |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

