.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, horse, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding, tennis, cricket
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who's sport is cricket is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the turtle##2
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the owner of the turtle is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is tennis is between the owner of the ferret and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | lizard | ferret   | turtle     | horse     |
| Sport   | snowboarding  | cricket | tennis   | skateboarding  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

