.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
House: art-deco, wooden, craftsman, futuristic
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, subway, skateboard, airplane
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the person driving the airplane is in an even position##4
2. the wooden house is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
5. the person driving the airplane is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the craftsman house is the person driving the taxi##1
7. the person driving the skateboard is the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| House   | art-deco  | futuristic   | craftsman     | wooden |
| Transport   | skateboard  | airplane      | taxi        | subway     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

