.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, comedy, time-travel, disaster
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, goat, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, jet-ski, van
1. the person watching disaster movies is the owner of the pony##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the bus is the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
5. the person driving the bus is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far right##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
9. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | drama   | disaster   | time-travel | comedy |
| Pet         | bird      | pony | hamster      | goat |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus        | van       | jet-ski  |

