.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, coffee, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, punk, jazz, reggae
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster, rat
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the fan of punk is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
8. the fan of reggae is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | coffee   | hot-chocolate      | soy-milk       | milk |
| Music-Genre   | country | reggae | jazz     | punk |
| Pet     | rat     | guinea-pig  | chinchilla | hamster |

