.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, van, taxi, scooter
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, camping, collecting
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goat, guinea-pig, horse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the owner of the goat is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the owner of the chinchilla##2
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person driving the van##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
5. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person driving the bike##1
8. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Transport      | taxi   | scooter          | van | bike        |
| Hobby   | camping     | chess | collecting   | puzzles     |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goat         | horse         | guinea-pig |

