.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, collecting, drawing, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, bus, boat, subway
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, chaman, old-henry, game
1. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
2. the person driving the boat is the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
5. the chaman-smoker is between the person driving the train and the person who's hobby is chess##2
6. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
7. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is chess is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | collecting | chess      | drawing       | singing    |
| Transport           | bus  | boat  | subway | train |
| Cigar   | game      | old-henry | chaman         | tiparillo    |

