.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, subway, quad-bike
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, magic-tricks, board-games, baking
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Transport   | snowmobile         | ship  | subway     | quad-bike         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Hobby      | magic-tricks         | board-games  | hiking   | baking |

