.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, quad-bike, taxi, boat
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
There 4 different types of food: potato, grapefruit, orange, garlic
 1. the person eating orange is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 2. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the scooter##2
 5. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 6. the person eating garlic is the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
 9. the malaysian is between the person driving the boat and the person driving the taxi##2
10. the person eating orange is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Transport   | scooter  | taxi    | quad-bike | boat    |
| Nationality   | canadian | nigerian | malaysian  | turkish |
| Food           | orange   | garlic    | potato        | grapefruit   |

