.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, rock-climbing, traveling, dancing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, cycling, biathlon, handball
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, italian, russian
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the russian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
4. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the indonesian##3
9. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby      | collecting                | dancing  | rock-climbing | traveling   |
| Sport           | handball | cycling | tennis   | biathlon |
| Nationality   | indonesian         | dutch     | russian     | italian |

