.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, chestnut, brown, orange
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, lemonade, milk
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
4. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person watching western movies and the person drinking milk##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Color          | brown    | chestnut  | orange  | blue |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | iced-tea     | milk    | fanta |

