.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, van, car
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, skiing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person driving the van and the argentine##2
2. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the person driving the bike##1
9. the turkish is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is baseball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Transport      | bike | van      | helicopter  | car    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Sport           | lacrosse      | skiing       | water-polo   | baseball      |

