.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
House: modern, victorian, cape-cod, wooden
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, september, july
1. the cape-cod house is in an even position##4
2. the victorian house is between the wooden house and the person who's birthday is in june##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
4. the wooden house is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the japanese is between the person who's birthday is in june and the australian##2
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| House         | modern    | cape-cod | victorian  | wooden  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Birthday         | september   | june      | july | november       |

