4. the person drinking cola is the chef##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
6. the dancer is the wooden house##1
7. the victorian house is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
8. the craftsman house is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
