.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, grapefruit, lemon, tomato
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, baccarat, bongani, pall-mall
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, hiking, skydiving
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person eating tomato##2
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | tomato  | cabbage   | lemon    |
| Cigar   | prince  | bongani     | pall-mall | baccarat |
| Hobby   | hiking   | skydiving | magic-tricks | card-games   |

