The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, d&b, indie, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, taxi, van, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
3. the fan of d&b is on the far left##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the trike##1
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person driving the van##1
7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
8. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| City   | edinburgh | nizza | boston | liverpool   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b    | jazz   | indie     | blues    |
| Transport   | taxi  | van | trike  | helicopter |

