.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, water-polo, volleyball, skateboarding
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, board-games, hiking, reading
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, aristoff, ritmeester, havana
1. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is reading is in an odd position##4
3. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is baking##3
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
7. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
8. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Sport    | volleyball    | water-polo    | lacrosse  | skateboarding |
| Hobby   | reading | board-games | baking | hiking      |
| Cigar     | aristoff   | swisher        | havana   | ritmeester       |

 